Package org.web3d.x3d.jsail.fields

Class SFMatrix3fObject

java.lang.Object
org.web3d.x3d.jsail.fields.X3DConcreteField
org.web3d.x3d.jsail.fields.SFMatrix3fObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Matrix3, SFMatrix3f, X3DField
public class SFMatrix3fObject
extends X3DConcreteField
implements SFMatrix3f
This utility class provides a concrete implementation corresponding to SFMatrix3f X3D field type.


Package hint: This specification class is defined by the X3D Java Language Binding Specification for the Scene Authoring Interface (SAI). SFMatrix3f specifies a 3x3 matrix of single-precision floating point numbers, organized in row-major fashion. Warning: comma characters in attribute values do not pass strict XML validation.

Related field object: MFMatrix3fObject
See Also:
X3D Tooltips: type SFMatrix3f, SAI Java Specification: B.4.11 X3DFieldTypes, SAI Abstract Specification: 5.2.15 SAIFieldType, X3D Abstract Specification: SFMatrix3fAndMFMatrix3f, X3D Tooltips, X3D Tooltips: field, X3D Tooltips: fieldValue, X3D Scene Authoring Hints
